  "texts": [
    "Unlike conventional models, this algorithm captures complex patterns and adapts to evolving data, reducing false positives and negatives.By leveraging ensemble methods, the anomaly detection algorithm captures a broader range of normal data patterns and better adapts to the dynamic nature of WSN data.",
    "Consequently, it becomes more effective at identifying subtle anomalies that may appear in diverse forms, reducing the risk of false positives and false negatives, thereby enhancing the overall anomaly detection performance.",
    "Ensemble methods for anomaly detection use various ML models as building blocks.",
    "The following models are combined in the ensemble to improve the performance: DT, RF, SVM, k-NN, and artificial neural networks (ANN).",
    "The choice of these base models is made based on the dataset and anomaly patterns."
